description.en:
Amane Fujimiya&rsquo;s neighbour in the apartment he lives in is the school&rsquo;s number one lovable angel: Excellent and with a level of beauty that can only be described as angelic &ndash; Mahiru Shiina. Amane, an ordinary student who doesn&rsquo;t stand out, is her neighbour, but until now, they didn&rsquo;t interact with each other. After meeting the soggy angel in the rain:

&ldquo;I&rsquo;m returning what I borrowed. By the way, clean up your room. It&rsquo;s filthy.&rdquo;

&ldquo;None of your business.&rdquo;

A relationship with a sharp-tongued angel begins, starting with handing over an umbrella. From catching a cold and having someone take care of you, to making a meal for someone because they neglected their health, to joint work (cleaning rooms)&hellip;

